{"title":"Next Gen Kask Utopia Aero Road Helmet Makes INEOS Faster By Covering their Ears","link":"https://bikerumor.com/next-gen-kask-utopia-aero-road-helmet-makes-ineos-faster-by-covering-their-ears/","date":1704309331000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, detail photo by Chris Auld\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Filippo Ganna and the INEOS Grenadiers give us a sneak peek at the next generation reshaping of the Kask Utopia aero road helmet. Its secret to more speed appears to be more coverage. Less extra coverage for extra coverage for improved safety. But instead, a cowl that smooths airflow over the rider’s ears, plus reshaped intake &amp; exhaust vents….</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sneak Peek: New Kask Utopia aero road helmet, coming soon</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photos by Chris Auld Russ Ellis, training camp ride front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-ride.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cauldphoto/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris Auld</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cyclingimages/\" target=\"_blank\">Russ Ellis</a>/<a href=\"https://www.ineosgrenadiers.com/article/gallery-2024-the-first-ride\" target=\"_blank\">INEOS Grenadiers</a>) </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Kask has not yet given us any new information about a design reboot to their top-tier Utopia aero road helmet. In fact, they just updated the classic <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kask-utopia-y-aero-road-bike-helmet/\" target=\"_blank\">Utopia Y</a> last spring, after half a decade of pro racing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But the INEOS Grenadiers team has been prominently showing off an all-new iteration of the aerodynamic lid across social media since they unveiled their new colors on January 1st. And the differences are quite extreme.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most notably, ear cowls.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new? And is it really a new Utopia?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photos by Chris Auld &amp; Russ Ellis, angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_angled-front.jpg 1440w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Officially we don’t know for sure that the new aero road helmet will retain the Kask Utopia name. But the overall profile – both from directly in front or the side – is similar enough, that I would go out on a limb and predict it will be still be a Utopia, maybe with a different letter tacked on the end. Think Utopia X, maybe?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photos by Chris Auld &amp; Russ Ellis, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_side.jpg 1500w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What Kask changed are: upgraded aerodynamics and smaller external vents. The new standout feature is a small fairing that drops down a bit at the sides to cover the top of the rider’s ears. Presumably, the goal like on their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kask-3d-shaped-custom-bambino-pro-evo-aero-helmet-for-gannas-hour-record/\" target=\"_blank\">Bambino Pro</a> TT helmet is to smooth airflow off the cyclist’s face or sunglasses, as it passes your bumpy ears. Interestingly, SunGod eyewear sponsor INEOS, not Kask’s own KOO. So perhaps KOO will also debut special sunglasses designed for even smoother aerodynamics.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photos by Chris Auld &amp; Russ Ellis, ear cowl detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_ear-cover-detail.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking at the various positioning on a few of the team riders’ heads, those with a closer fit of the helmet appear to have this cowl pressing their ears a bit back against their heads. While riders that might have sized up on their helmet seem to have more room for their ears.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ll certainly be curious to see how comfortable this is. And how big the aero gains are, once the helmet officially launches. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What else do we know?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photos by Chris Auld &amp; Russ Ellis, front riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_front-riding.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The ear covers are the most striking change. But Kask really completely changed the vent layout, as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The 3 lower front-facing vents are mostly unchanged. But Kask shifted the top vent further forward. And they completely removed the 2 upper side vents. This completely shales up Kask’s ‘Hyvent’ concept. But presumably means much smoother aerodynamics, especially as the rider changes head position.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photo by Chris Auld, rear view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-rear-view.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the back, there is still a sharp pointed tail. But now unsurprisingly, the 3 rear exhaust vents have been pinched down to a much smaller height, matching the reduced intake vent area on the front. Kask currently rates the Utopia Y as 4/5 for ventilation. We’d guess this new one is more like a 3/5.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photo by Russ Ellis, training camp ride side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp-group-ride.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The INEOS team are also seen in the fully-vented all-rounder <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-kask-elemento-helmet/\" target=\"_blank\">Elemento</a> which debuted last summer promising maximum aero benefits and 5/5 ventilation. We also just so happened to publish <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kask-elemento-helmet-review-3d-printed-padding/\" target=\"_blank\">a full review of that lid</a> today, as well.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, detail photo by Chris Auld\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Chris-Auld_training-camp-side-detail.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>From a final details and safety point of view, this new version of the Utopia still uses a similar 2-piece in-mold construction like the current helmet. And it looks like the same adjustable Octofit+ dial retention. And there’s a round red <a href=\"https://www.kask.com/en-it/kask-rotational-impact-wg11-test.html\" target=\"_blank\">WG11</a> sticker on the back. So it meets Kask’s own rotational impact protection standard, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How soon is coming soon for a new Kask Utopia?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Utopia X sneak peek, next gen aero road helmet ridden by INEOS Grenadiers, photo by Russ Ellis, training camp ride front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_front.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As for when it will be available, how light it will be, or how much it will cost? We don’t have any concrete data. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_ridden-by-INEOS-Grenadiers_photo-by-Russ-Ellis_December-team-training-camp_side.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kask-Utopia-X-sneak-peek_next-gen-aero-road-helmet_r